00:11:15,687 --> 00:11:19,756
Peter Rabbit, Roger Rabbit.
Valentino Wolowitz Rabbit.

251
00:11:21,426 --> 00:11:24,160
Oh, look at all that
chest hair and overbite.

252
00:11:24,162 --> 00:11:25,929
Of course you're a Wolowitz.

253
00:11:25,931 --> 00:11:27,864
(both laugh)

254
00:11:27,866 --> 00:11:30,066
Son of a bitch! He bit me!

255
00:11:30,068 --> 00:11:31,968
Are you okay?

256
00:11:31,970 --> 00:11:33,336
No, I'm not okay!

257
00:11:33,338 --> 00:11:35,238
Wild rabbits
can have rabies!

258
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:38,074
Oh. Well, why did you put
your finger near its mouth?

259
00:11:38,076 --> 00:11:40,910
Poor judgment, obviously.

260
00:11:40,912 --> 00:11:44,514
He's so little. I'm sure it's fine.
How can it be fine?

261
00:11:44,516 --> 00:11:48,118
I just got attacked by a clearly
anti-Semitic wild animal.

262
00:11:50,389 --> 00:11:54,457
It's not what we planned,
but this isn't so bad, right?

263
00:11:54,459 --> 00:11:57,927
It is freaking amazing.

264
00:11:57,929 --> 00:12:00,463
Well, glad
you're feeling better.

265
00:12:00,465 --> 00:12:02,499
I was just hungry and cranky,

266
00:12:02,501 --> 00:12:05,001
