When's it start?

339
00:15:20,332 --> 00:15:22,198
Midnight.

340
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:23,900
Midnight. Really?

341
00:15:23,902 --> 00:15:25,768
You know what? Let's do it.

342
00:15:25,770 --> 00:15:27,337
Okay, great!

343
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:30,840
