and have him tested.
Good.

352
00:15:48,827 --> 00:15:51,194
Thank you. Oh, okay,
there is a test!

353
00:15:51,196 --> 00:15:53,196
All they have to do is...

354
00:15:53,198 --> 00:15:55,231
