and check his brain.

355
00:15:55,233 --> 00:15:57,367
Oh, cut off his head?

356
00:15:57,369 --> 00:16:01,137
That's where
his little nose is.

357
00:16:01,139 --> 00:16:04,440
He's not showing
any symptoms.

358
00:16:04,442 --> 00:16:08,211
I guess I'll just go to the
emergency room to be safe.

359
00:16:08,213 --> 00:16:10,480
Howie, this is just
your hypochondria.

360
00:16:10,482 --> 00:16:12,482
No, when I sat
on the mute button

361
00:16:12,484 --> 00:16:15,051
