00:18:19,077 --> 00:18:21,477
We are young and fun!

402
00:18:21,479 --> 00:18:25,214
(horn honking)

403
00:18:26,785 --> 00:18:28,818
I stand corrected.

404
00:18:28,820 --> 00:18:31,320
<i>Fun.</i>

405
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:43,075
